<h1>Arnold Electric Services — Fleet Wrap Video Review & Testimonial</h1>
<p>Watch Arnold Electric Services share their first-hand experience working with Chicago Fleet Wraps on a full fleet wrap installation. The project featured Hi-Vis reflective vinyl on their commercial service vans, combining professional branding with enhanced safety visibility for their electrical service crews working in low-light conditions.</p>
<p>From the initial design consultation through final installation, hear directly from the client about the quality of materials, the professionalism of the Chicago Fleet Wraps crew, and the impact the finished graphics have had on their business visibility and brand recognition throughout Chicagoland.</p>
<p>Chicago Fleet Wraps specializes in commercial fleet wraps for electrical contractors, HVAC companies, plumbers, and other trade service businesses across Chicago and the surrounding suburbs. Using premium Avery Dennison and 3M vinyl, every installation is built to last 5&ndash;7 years and designed to turn heads on the road.</p>
